{"type":"assistant.message","data":{"messageId":"834d9690-5a63-4397-86ae-c412a712dfd6","content":"**The issue: MAUI has no per-request scope.**\n\nIn ASP.NET Core, `AddScoped` creates a new instance per HTTP request — each request is a natural scope boundary. In MAUI, there's no equivalent automatic scope. The app essentially has one long-lived scope, so `AddScoped` behaves like `AddSingleton`. Your DbContext lives forever, accumulating tracked entities across navigations.\n\n**Fixes:**\n\n1. **Use `AddTransient<MyDbContext>()`** — new instance each time it's injected.\n\n2. **Create manual scopes** where needed:\n   ```csharp\n   using var scope = serviceScopeFactory.CreateScope();\n   var db = scope.ServiceProvider.GetRequiredService<MyDbContext>();\n   ```\n\n3. **Use a DbContext factory** (recommended):\n   ```csharp\n   // Registration\n   services.AddDbContextFactory<MyDbContext>(opts => ...);\n\n   // Usage\n   using var db = dbContextFactory.CreateDbContext();\n   ```\n\nOption 3 is the cleanest — it gives you explicit, short-lived DbContext instances without leaking change-tracker state across pages.","toolRequests":[],"interactionId":"2da939cc-3a06-4c11-9e31-837d436be2d4","reasoningOpaque":"","reasoningText":"The user is asking about a common issue when migrating from ASP.NET Core to .NET MAUI regarding dependency injection scoping, specifically with `AddScoped` and DbContext lifetime behavior.\n\nThis is a conceptual question I can answer directly without needing to search any codebase.\n\nThe key issue: In ASP.NET Core, `AddScoped` creates a new instance per HTTP request (each request is a \"scope\"). In MAUI, there's no per-request scope — the app has a single long-lived scope, so `AddScoped` effectively behaves like `AddSingleton`. This means the DbContext lives for the entire app lifetime, accumulating tracked entities and stale data across navigations.","outputTokens":449,"requestId":"9424:EB431:145EC70:16DB9D9:6A0673A1"},"id":"5dbb85c1-b900-4968-963b-247c520b1519","timestamp":"2026-05-15T01:15:23.908Z","parentId":"50b49a2e-7b87-4bfe-9535-05b3a0bc1f40"}
